children.subject: I see that a lot of people have seen this post, but not many have responded yet. The survey is very short and should only take about 5 minutes to complete. I need to reach out to at least 40 people by Tuesday night, so I'd be really grateful if everyone could take a few minutes and respond to the survey. Thanks!

history.content:
Hello,

My name is Khalid Durani and I am an EECS student here at Cal. I hope everyone is doing great and enjoying a restful Thanksgiving break! I am writing in this forum to request the participation of my fellow EECS students in a survey for my PSYCH 133 project. The topic of my project is the detrimental effects of sleep deprivation. I would greatly appreciate it if everyone could fill out the Google form linked below, which also includes a brochure about the benefits of adequate sleep and the consequences of sleep loss. Thank you in advance!

Survey: https://forms.gle/ugBV81HyP61JqFnK6

Kind regards,
Khalid Durani
history.subject: PSYCH 133 Outreach survey
